{"id": "jcy1665702866875", "title": "Browser Displays a Red Error Page", "breadcrumbs": ["Developing Web Applications", "Deploying Uniface Web Applications", "Web Application Errors", "Uniface WRD Configuration Errors", "Browser Displays a Red Error Page"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcy1665702866875.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Browser Displays a Red Error Page</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: Server Pages are not Displayed Correctly \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: Server Pages are not Displayed Correctly \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwh1665702866803.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:  Errors Reported in Browser \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:  Errors Reported in Browser \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/odf1665702867006.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcy1665702866875.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcy1665702866875.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcy1665702866875.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jcy1665702866875.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jcy1665702866875.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jcy1665702866875.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jcy1665702866875\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Depending on the specific error, the browser may display HTTP 4xx or 5xx status codes\n      in the debug console. The following table outlines common causes and recommended resolutions\n      for these errors.</p>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d917e1_d918e1_d919e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e49\"> Error: 400 URD_BAD_REQUEST Bad request detected by WRD in HTTP server </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__d5958e20\">Bad HTTP request, data size is larger than the maximum\n        allowed size. Please contact your system administrator.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__d5958e23\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__d5958e23__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__d5958e23__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__d5958e23__entry__1\">The content data size of the request is larger than the value of parameter\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">MAXPOSTDATASIZE</span>. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__d5958e23__entry__2\">If the large data size of a request is necessary based on your application\n                logic, adjust the value of the servlet parameter <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">MAXPOSTDATASIZE</span>.\n                Otherwise, talk with your network administrator. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d920e1_d921e1_d922e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e98\"> Error : 300 URD_MW_ERROR Middleware: UV8 Error: -24 </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_n1r_pg4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_n1r_pg4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_n1r_pg4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_n1r_pg4_hwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">userver.exe</span> cannot be started. Error -24,\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">NETERR_START_SERVER</code>, is returned if URouter could not\n                        create a UServer process, for example, because the executable was not\n                        found.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_n1r_pg4_hwb__entry__2\">\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__ol_gns_kh4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11372e1_d11373e1_d11374e1\">Specify correct location for\n                              Uniface Server in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.asn</span> file. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11375e1_d11376e1_d11377e1\">Stop the Uniface Router service. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11378e1_d11379e1_d11380e1\">Restart the Uniface Router\n                              service. </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d923e1_d924e1_d925e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e158\"> Error: 300 URD_MW_ERROR Middleware: UV8 Error#: -25 </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_yhp_rg4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_yhp_rg4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_yhp_rg4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_yhp_rg4_hwb__entry__1\">Server assignment file cannot be found.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_yhp_rg4_hwb__entry__2\">\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__ol_kkf_3h4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11384e1_d11385e1_d11386e1\">Check the UST entry for UServer in\n                              the [SERVERS] section of <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.asn</span>For\n                                 example:<p class=\"p\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__p_d23144e1_d23145e1_d23146e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">myust = d:/u8/bin/userver.exe /asn = userver.asn /dir =\n                                    d:/u8/Project/web</code>\n</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11387e1_d11388e1_d11389e1\">Also check whether the specified\n                              UST assignment file exists in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">/adm</span> directory,\n                              or in the directory specified in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/dir</code> switch. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11390e1_d11391e1_d11392e1\">Stop URouter via Services. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11393e1_d11394e1_d11395e1\">Start URouter via Services. </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d926e1_d927e1_d928e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e227\"> Error: 300 URD_MW_ERROR Middleware: UV8 Error#: Failure in the connection to the\n            Uniface Application Server  </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__p_d23147e1_d23148e1_d23149e1\">\n<samp class=\"ph msgph\">Error Text: Cannot connect to the Uniface process on the remote address/port.\n                             \n Error ID: <var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</samp>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_mlj_sg4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_mlj_sg4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_mlj_sg4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_mlj_sg4_hwb__entry__1\">URouter is not running.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_mlj_sg4_hwb__entry__2\">\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__ol_y33_fh4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11399e1_d11400e1_d11401e1\">Start URouter via Services. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__li_d11402e1_d11403e1_d11404e1\">Check the web server log files for\n                              the precise error. </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d929e1_d930e1_d931e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e285\"> Error: 213 URD_ACCESS_DENIED Access denied. </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_hlf_bh4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_hlf_bh4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_hlf_bh4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_hlf_bh4_hwb__entry__1\">preRequest trigger or preActivate trigger returns\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">$status=-21</code> when, for example, the wrong password is\n                        provided. The WRD should redisplay logon form when\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">$status=-21</code> is returned by UServer.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_hlf_bh4_hwb__entry__2\">Specify correct username and password.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d932e1_d933e1_d934e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e332\"> Error: 212 URD_PROVIDE_AUTH User-name and password were not provided. </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_t55_sg4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_t55_sg4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible causes</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_t55_sg4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_t55_sg4_hwb__entry__1\">On Logon screen, Cancel button is pressed with empty username and\n                              password.<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">OR</strong></p><p class=\"p\">BASIC authentication scheme is not\n                           supported or is disabled by the Web browser.</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_t55_sg4_hwb__entry__2\">Specify username.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__section_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d856718e377\"> Error: 103 URD_NO_NEW_APP Server: A new application could not be established. </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_pr1_tg4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_pr1_tg4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__table_pr1_tg4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_pr1_tg4_hwb__entry__1\">The middleware module <code class=\"ph codeph\">UV8</code> is not specified in the\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">MIDDLEWARE</code> servlet setting. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jcy1665702866875__table_pr1_tg4_hwb__entry__2\">\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"jcy1665702866875__ol_pxp_vg4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">Specify <code class=\"ph codeph\">MIDDLEWARE=UV8:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var>|</code> ... </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Stop and restart the web server (for example, Tomcat). </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Try the Server Page again. </li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Browser Displays a Red Error Page Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Depending on the specific error, the browser may display HTTP 4xx or 5xx status codes in the debug console. The following table outlines common causes and recommended resolutions for these errors. Error: 400 URD_BAD_REQUEST Bad request detected by WRD in HTTP server Bad HTTP request, data size is larger than the maximum allowed size. Please contact your system administrator. Possible cause Resolution The content data size of the request is larger than the value of parameter MAXPOSTDATASIZE . If the large data size of a request is necessary based on your application logic, adjust the value of the servlet parameter MAXPOSTDATASIZE . Otherwise, talk with your network administrator. Error : 300 URD_MW_ERROR Middleware: UV8 Error: -24 Possible cause Resolution userver.exe cannot be started. Error -24, NETERR_START_SERVER , is returned if URouter could not create a UServer process, for example, because the executable was not found. Specify correct location for Uniface Server in the urouter.asn file. Stop the Uniface Router service. Restart the Uniface Router service. Error: 300 URD_MW_ERROR Middleware: UV8 Error#: -25 Possible cause Resolution Server assignment file cannot be found. Check the UST entry for UServer in the [SERVERS] section of urouter.asn For example: myust = d:/u8/bin/userver.exe /asn = userver.asn /dir = d:/u8/Project/web Also check whether the specified UST assignment file exists in the /adm directory, or in the directory specified in the /dir switch. Stop URouter via Services. Start URouter via Services. Error: 300 URD_MW_ERROR Middleware: UV8 Error#: Failure in the connection to the Uniface Application Server Error Text: Cannot connect to the Uniface process on the remote address/port. Error ID: Number Possible cause Resolution URouter is not running. Start URouter via Services. Check the web server log files for the precise error. Error: 213 URD_ACCESS_DENIED Access denied. Possible cause Resolution preRequest trigger or preActivate trigger returns $status=-21 when, for example, the wrong password is provided. The WRD should redisplay logon form when $status=-21 is returned by UServer. Specify correct username and password. Error: 212 URD_PROVIDE_AUTH User-name and password were not provided. Possible causes Resolution On Logon screen, Cancel button is pressed with empty username and password. OR BASIC authentication scheme is not supported or is disabled by the Web browser. Specify username. Error: 103 URD_NO_NEW_APP Server: A new application could not be established. Possible cause Resolution The middleware module UV8 is not specified in the MIDDLEWARE servlet setting. Specify MIDDLEWARE=UV8: Host | ... Stop and restart the web server (for example, Tomcat). Try the Server Page again. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}